Description: Next-gen container runtime with zero-copy DAG storage and P2P image sync
 A content-addressed workload execution system. Run OCI images as Linux
 containers (runc), Firecracker microVMs, or Apple Silicon VMs.
 .
 Features:
  - Zero-copy DAG store with rkyv + memmap2
  - P2P block sync across nodes (Bloom filter + gRPC)
  - Native Dockerfile build engine (no Docker required)
  - Compose support (up/down/logs/build)
  - Encrypted secrets (AES-256-GCM) and configs

